    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.5.2">
<l>pūṇṭavattam piṟarkkaṭaintu toṇṭu paṭṭup poynūlai meynūleṉ ṟeṉṟu mōti</l>
<l>māṇṭavattam pōkātē vammi ṉentai yeṉvaṇaṅkap paṭuvāṉai kaṇaṅka ḷēttum</l>
<l>nīṇṭavattaik karumukilai yemmāṉ taṉṉai niṉṟavūr nittilattait tottār cōlai</l>
<l>kāṇṭavattaik kaṉalerivāyp peyvit tāṉaik kaṇṭatunāṉ kaṭalmallait talaca yaṉattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come [here] without persisting in [this] nonsense,</l>
<l rend="indent">tiring [from] always chanting, calling a book of lies a book of truth,</l>
<l>Resorting to others, being enslaved, fettered in nonsense!</l>
<l rend="indent">My beholding of the one who is adored [by] me [as] father,</l>
<l>The vast entity which multitudes praise, dark cloud, our lord,</l>
<l rend="indent">pearl of Niṉṟavūr, the one who made flames rain</l>
<l>[From] the mouth of the fire god on the cluster-filled forest, Khāṇḍava,</l>
<l rend="indent">was in Talacayaṉam at Mallai by the sea.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
